# SMOKE CHECKS FOR FAST API

## Start the Server
export MODEL_ARTIFACT=model/pipeline.joblib
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

## Is the process up ?
curl -s http://localhost:8000/healthcheck | jq

Expected Response:
{
  "status": "ok",
  "model_loaded": true,
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "expected_features": [
    "type",
    "amount",
    "amount_log",
    "tx_count_2h",
    "tx_count_6h",
    "tx_avg_amt_2h",
    "tx_sum_amt_6h",
    "tx_max_amt_2h",
    "hours_since_last_tx",
    "tx_count_so_far",
    "is_returning_user"
  ]
}

## Check to see if the model is ready ?

Expected Response:
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
date: Tue, 26 Aug 2025 09:49:13 GMT
server: uvicorn
content-length: 36
content-type: application/json

If 503, the model failed to load (check MODEL_ARTIFACT path)

